A fierce, red, armored wasp flying in mid-air, looking at the viewer, aiming multiple weapons at the viewer with its mechanical arms. Its heavy armor is intricately detailed with scratches and glowing red accents, giving it a wild and menacing look. On its chest, the word 'Buzz' is boldly engraved or painted, standing out against its armor. Dust and debris rise from the ground beneath it, creating a dynamic sense of motion as it hovers aggressively. Its large, translucent wings buzz with energy, casting faint, flickering shadows around it.

Above its head, a speech bubble reads: 'Looking for me?!' The background is dim and dramatic, with swirling clouds and faint rays of sunlight breaking through, enhancing the tension and focus on the wasp. The ground below shows cracks and dirt, further emphasizing the intensity of its takeoff.

Side view portrait of an ancient Grim Reaper-like figure looking away from viewer standing in a desolate wasteland, wearing a dark, decaying cloak, holding a large scythe. The blade of the scythe has a faint glowing green energy, tendrils of light swirling from the blade, cracked earth and faint black mist beneath, skeletal face shrouded in shadow, mystical and grim, epic dark fantasy art style. His cloak swirls in the wind.
